contact.content:
My name is Jay Ann and I am a highly trained real estate professional with years of experience. I am a member of the National Association of Realtors and a PRC Accredited Real Estate Salesperson. I work hard to ensure that you are getting the best deal possible on your new home or investment property.

Being a real estate agent is more than just listing and selling homes. It is about understanding the needs and wants of my clients, as well as anticipating their needs for the future.

I am knowledgeable about the local market, including school districts, neighborhoods and local amenities. I will assist you with all aspects of buying or selling a home and can help you get through the process as quickly as possible.

I strive to provide excellent customer service and communication throughout your real estate transaction. This allows me to build relationships and trust with my clients so that when they need assistance in the future, I can provide it to them with ease.
Connect with me and let's discuss how I can help you!
